{
  "stem": "10587.2",
  "chunk_idx": 2,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And some of it was even classical music, because we had a-- I remember the-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] one tenor whose name was Yom Kippur.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "He was quite-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] the young people liked to listen to it.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] So I used to-- I was in charge of the microphone-- of the gramophone.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And we had a little radio which we would also listen to.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably more Jewish and whatever they were dancing in those days, maybe tango and [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] waltz or polka.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "No.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No, that I experienced after.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 15,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[LAUGHS]",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yes, we heard on the radio.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We also-- it was written in the papers as well as-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] but the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and we were concerned about it.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember my father talking about that.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] But they felt that, you know, being who they are and where they are, that maybe nothing would happen to them.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was a big mistake.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That-- because I remember when they were talking about these things and-- and even I-- I used to read the papers quite a bit, whatever paper we had in Oswiecim, because I was fascinated prior to that how, for so many years, the Japanese and the Chinese were fighting, you know, and so many people were killed.",
      "word_count": 57
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "All this was taking place, and the Poles in the parliament were talking about the shechita.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I don't know if you-- the [HEBREW] means how you slaughter animal, like for food, you know.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they did not-- they were discussing it that the Jews should not-- you cannot shoot the animal.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It has to be slaughtered by a shochet.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And that's what they were occupied with.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "Because not too long after that, I was listening to the radio where they were-- where the Germans were getting ready to occupy Poland.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And to-- listening to the radio was like a comedy, that they had [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] passwords like [POLISH].",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then we could see-- they had little tanks.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "We could see the tanks.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "They were totally disorganized.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And the horses pulling the-- the-- the cannons.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "But they mainly, the little tanks, like maybe one or two man tank, probably one man tank.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And when they would say [POLISH], they would go one direction.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "When they would say [POLISH], they would say-- go in the other direction.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "It was total chaos.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Yeah, I was 12 years old.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "There was anticipation and worries and concern, and a lot of talk about it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But unfortunately no action.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "No one took any action.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 19,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Maybe some people did.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "The summer of 1939, I remember that the-- Marshal Pilsudski died and the-- [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] I think  it was 1939.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And they elected a new marshal, which was a protege to-- his name was Smigly-Rydz-- took the place.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And they were singing songs about how they're going to fight the Germans.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they would take an example from the Smigly-Rydz, they would-- and that they are ready for them, but they were-- really didn't.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "The Polish Army was always terrific when it came to prepare a parade because they had those white horses, [INAUDIBLE], pulling the cannons.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 20,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "But when the German came, the white horses were muddy and couldn't get a-- pull the cannons out of the mud.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I don't think it was any different.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And-- maybe there was more participa-- anticipation of something that is-- that will be happening, of the war, that the war will come.",
      "word_count": 23
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They did not know exactly when.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 21,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "But life was normal as always, with the exception of this concern.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "When the invasion occurred, we were-- I was-- yes, I remember.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "When the invasion occurred, we had-- there was some-- excuse me.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] There were some wagons with troops, Polish troops, that pulled in into-- into our building, to the square of my grandfather's building.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And they locked the gate.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "And they took off the Polish uniform, and underneath there was a German uniform.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That's how well they-- I remember this, and I was-- and I saw it with my own eyes.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "The Poles never had a chance because they were infiltrated.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Because the area where I was born, that was Silesia, and it was always either Poland or German.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "The language was going back and forth.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So they were-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] they were Germans that could speak Polish as well as the German language.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And-- and I was amazed when I saw what was happening in a-- in a few hours.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] The city was occupied by the Germans.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 22,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I don't remember any bombing or destruction or any kind in Oswiecim.",
      "word_count": 12
    }
  ],
